<br>
&quot;One of the great things about Planes of Power is that it will once again bring back the ability to form pick-up groups and 6 person groups and still be able to engage in raid level encounters...while there will still be encounters tailored to the current system of en-masse or large guild raids, we are trying hard to make the new high level content as accessible to players as we can.&quot;<br>
